      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How Can You Access Free Internet With Government Aid?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<p>Seeking affordable or free internet? Government programs are here to assist low-income families, seniors, and the disabled. With an EBT card, living in Section 8 housing, or receiving SSI, these programs provide the essential internet services, ensuring access to crucial online resources. See which program is the best for you!</p>\n<img alt=\"How Can You Access Free Internet With Government Aid?_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
