      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How Can You Access Free Internet With Government Aid?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. What Is The Lifeline Internet Program? </h4>\n<p>Designed for the elderly, disabled, and low-income families on public assistance, it ensures vital internet connectivity. This program bridges the digital divide, providing necessary access to the internet for those in need.</p>\n<img alt=\"How Can You Access Free Internet With Government Aid?_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid/how-can-you-access-free-internet-with-government-aid_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
